                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6028" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1521</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8465 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化疫为机：迈瑞医疗呼吸机爆单之解</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Analysis on Mindray Ventilator&#39;s Hot Sale: Crisis Transform of Circumstance under COVID-19</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄怡，何盼盼，范自诚，何溦，郭诗桐，桑洁丽，吴培宏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳迈瑞生物医疗电子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情；迈瑞医疗；运营管理；组织即兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">COVID-19；Mindray；Operation Management；Organizational Improvisation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年初，突如其来的新冠疫情打乱了全球市场既有的发展节奏，各个行业原有的 产业结构、生态布局与生产秩序发生了巨大改变。迈瑞医疗作为国内呼吸机行业的龙头企 业，疫情的爆发使得公司生命信息与支持业务的呼吸机、监护仪等产品的需求量大幅增长， 超出公司原有的生产预期与产能极限。本案例阐述了疫情对公司所处的外部环境与内部业 务结构的影响，阐明公司在原材料供应、生产、物流以及技术研发等环节采取的一系列调 整措施，分析其取得的成效及未来可能面对的问题，旨在引导学员透过案例资料了解组织 即兴行为特征、企业决策机制、产品全生命周期管理的要点以及经营风险的识别与应对， 提高分析与解决问题能力，也就迈瑞医疗的成功经验为其它企业提供有益参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the beginning of 2020, the sudden outbreak of COVID-19 disrupted the existing development rhythm of the global market, and the original industrial structure, ecological layout and production order of various industries were greatly changed by the outbreak. Mindray Medical is a leading enterprise in the ventilator industry in China. The outbreak of the epidemic has greatly increased the demand for the ventilator, monitor and other products of the company&#39;s life information and support business, which has exceeded the original production expectation and capacity limit of the company. In this case, the impact of the epidemic on the external environment and internal business structure of the company is introduced in detail, and the company has taken a series of targeted adjustment measures in the links of raw material supply, manufacturing, logistics and technology research and development, and discusses its achievements and possible problems in the future. It aims to guide students to understand the concept of organizational improvisation, enterprise decision-making mechanism, key points of product lifecycle management, and the identification and response of operational risks through the given cases and materials, in order to improve the corresponding ability to analyze and solve problems. At the same time, it also provides reference for other enterprises on Mindray&#39;s successful experience.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略与风险管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织即兴行为特征、 社会责任理论、 协调效应、 产品全生命周期管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
